           SHORT="Database abstraction layer for guile"
cat << EOF
guile-dbi is a database generic interface. The main lib provide a way to use 
dbds (data base drivers) which are linked at run-time (like perl dbi or php 
or...).
This provide a very flexible way to use guile scheme implementation for db works. 
EOF
